sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Old Primary
    participant D as DCS quorum
    participant R as Best Replica
    participant H as HAProxy
    participant G as Go App

    O-xD: 无法续约 Leader Lock
    O-xG: 旧连接超时/Reset/57P01
    D->>D: TTL 到期，Leader Key 可竞争
    R->>D: 读取成员、Timeline、LSN、同步资格
    R->>D: CAS 获取 Leader Lock
    R->>R: pre_promote 调用 Fencing
    R->>O: STONITH/撤销网络或存储访问
    R->>R: pg_promote，生成新 Timeline
    H->>R: /primary 返回 200
    H-xO: 标记 down，关闭旧会话
    G->>G: 有界退避 + Jitter，重建连接
    G->>R: 新事务；未知 Commit 先按幂等键对账
